[0,x] \implies \exists \xi \in (0,x)
\begin{align} &g(x) - g(0) = g'(\xi) (x - 0) = (1 + c f'(\xi)) x \ge (1 - ck)x\\ \implies & g(x) \ge g(0) + (1 - ck) x \end{align}
